item.title: BUET CSE Fest Hackathon 2019
item.description: We were still the juniormost batch then . Our CSE ‘14 was arranging a Grand CSE Fest and this was the first time this kind of inter university hackathon was happening . But the topics of the hackathon were not our forte . But we still thought about giving it a go . And boy ! we never regret that . Me , alongside with Najib and Apurba formed a team .
